  .quote
    %strong "Truth will rise above falsehood as oil above water."
    %cite -- Miguel de Cervantes
  %ul
    %li.slide
      %p
        %strong Statement:
        Why don't we dig it all up, like the Aussies‽
    %li.slide
      %p
        %strong Sir Paul's Assertion:
      %p Sell our National Soul.
      %p Dig up all our land, sacrificing our image for such short term gains.
    %li.slide
      %p
        %strong Our Response:
      %p Using the most optimistic measures, how much longer can New Zealand mine?
      %p About half the turnover of mining goes towards GDP.
      %p Dig up all of New Zealand and get 30% increase in GDP for a single year
    %li.slide
